name: Affliction Limited Edition Shredded Leather Jacket Skulls
description:
Limited Edition Affliction Shredded Leather Jacket Skulls Randy Couture UFC MMA


The perfect biker jacket

Color black. Size X-Large. Lightly used, missing one skull button $225.

Overview
Affliction's Shredded Jacket (MSRP $700) is a limited edition and hand-numbered piece made of 100-percent leather. It features a vintage fit with custom skull embroidery on the front with the company name hand-tooled on the back, skull zipper pulls also made of leather, and custom skull buttons. For added support and protection, the jacket features custom web elbow patches as well as convenient exterior and interior pockets.
